---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Sponsor">
  <h2 class="page-heading">Sponsor a Meeting</h2>
  <div class="card">
    <p>Sponsoring DC402 is a great way to give back to the community and foster growth of the group.</p>
    <h3>How it works</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Meeting sponsors may commit to picking up the tab at the end of the meeting.</li>
      <li>Alternately, a sponsor may elect to purchase a fixed food and/or drink menu; details must be announced 2 weeks prior.</li>
      <li>Sponsors may open the meeting with brief remarks (under 5 minutes, timed).</li>
      <li>Sponsor information may be distributed in written form and/or included in the meeting announcement.</li>
      <li>Sponsors are encouraged but not required to have a technical talk or presence.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Interested? Reach out at <a href="mailto:info@dc402.org">info@dc402.org</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .card p, .card li { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .card h3 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 1.25rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .card ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .card a { color: var(--accent); }
</style>
